ode> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSSStyleRule représente une règle de style CSS unique. Il implémente l'interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> avec une valeur de type 1 (CSSRule STYLE_RULE).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<p>La syntaxe est décrite à l'aide du format WebIDL.</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">interface CSSStyleRule : CSSRule {\n    attribute DOMString selectorText;\n    readonly attribute CSSStyleDeclaration style;\n};\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssstylerule.selectortext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule/selectorText\"><code>CSSStyleRule.selectorText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Obtient la représentation textuelle du sélecteur pour cette règle, par exemple \"H1, H2\".</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstylerule.style_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule/style\"><code>CSSStyleRule.style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne l'objet <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a> pour cette règle.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-cssstylerule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'CSSStyleRule' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Version de travail</span></td>\n      <td>pas de changement</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSStyleRule\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'CSSRule' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleRule","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntaxe","id":"syntaxe"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"}],"summary":"CSSStyleRule représente une règle de style CSS unique. Il implémente l'interface CSSRule (en-US) avec une valeur de type 1 (CSSRule STYLE_RULE).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleRule","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleRule","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSSStyleRule","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSStyleRule","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/cssstylerule","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/css